          <p>Complete well pump installation, repair, and pressure tank service. We keep your water flowing reliably year-round.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Drain Cleaning</h3>
          <p>Professional drain cleaning to clear stubborn clogs and restore proper flow in sinks, tubs, showers, and floor drains.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0H9"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Water Heaters</h3>
          <p>Sales, installation, and repair of water heaters. We help you choose the right unit and ensure efficient, reliable hot water.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Sump Pumps</h3>
          <p>Sump and ejector pump installation, repair, and replacement. Protect your basement from flooding and sewage backup.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Bathroom Remodeling</h3>
          <p>Complete bathroom and kitchen plumbing for remodeling projects. Expert fixture installation and pipe work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="services-more">
        <a href="/hugo-plumbing/services" class="btn btn--secondary">View All Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

